Current licensing posture
-------------------------

The current combined work includes `src/core/bitknit2.js`, which derives from
`neptuwunium/Knit` under EUPL-1.2. Until that implementation is replaced with a
non-EUPL-derived implementation, distribute this repository and any package
containing it under EUPL-1.2.

The official English EUPL-1.2 text is published by the European Commission at:

https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/sites/default/files/custom-page/attachment/eupl_v1.2_en.pdf

Future MIT target
-----------------

CarbonEngineJS intends to re-license this package under MIT once the
EUPL-derived BitKnit implementation is replaced or removed and the remaining
code and dependencies permit MIT distribution.

That future intent is not the current license. Treat EUPL-1.2 as the effective
license until a later commit replaces this file and the package metadata.
